<h2>Family</h2>
<p>
  A concrete member of the <a href="/blocks/dialog/">dialog family</a>
  (<code>droplist : dropdown :: dialog : drawer</code>). Its siblings are the centered <em>modal</em>
  (<code>placement: center</code>) and the bottom <em>sheet</em> (<code>placement: bottom</code>) — distinct
  members, distinct placements, one shared substrate.
</p>
